ollision Avoidance System, which is designed to reduce incidents of controlled flight into terrain which is responsible for 75 percent of all F-16 pilot fatalities.""The system predicts imminent collision and performs flight maneuvers to avoid ground impact."SOURCES:  Lockheed Martin,https://www.lockheedmartin.com/en-us/products/f-16.html***]]></description>
