s making them susceptible to being utilized by the CCP.""If successful, the cable could grant U.S. companies greater access to other developing markets in Asia, such as the Philippines and Malaysia." SOURCES: Business Insiderhttps://www.businessinsider.com/us-officials-may-undersea-cable-china-google-facebook-backed-wsj-2019-8***]]></description>
